snippet.title: Speed Dating for Ghosts Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy Game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/746400/Speed_Dating_for_Ghosts/

The official launch trailer for Speed Dating for Ghosts, a weird little dating sim by Ben Gelinas and Mikey Hamm. 

Note: This is a newer version with better audio.
